snippet.textDisplay:
Do you know what love is , dear ? 
          Love is a situation , where peace is found...
But today's lovers fight to get love ,
          And turn peace into the ground...

In love , even the simple words of a lover 
          seem like a sweet song...
but without love , even the sweetest song 
          in a lover's voice seems hoarse & wrong...

                -: Bappaditya Malik :-
                           ❤❤❤
